	dumpkeys will show  all key  maps  ,

all keys are in /usr/share/kbd/keymaps/ ,  you can choose them


you can change the default under /usr/share/kbd/keymaps ,or just use loadkeys then input your own set ,or use xmodmap ? 
ans:  change keymaps ,and load in /etc/vconsole


